body:
### DylDoge's GitHub Page

**Hey reader! My name is Dylan, and welcome to my GitHub page!**

I am a Java developer who usually codes server plugins/modifications for [Minecraft](minecraft.net), with aid from the popular server API, [Spigot](spigotmc.org). This website will simply be a host for any plugins I create, directly from my GitHub account.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
